isRobotOverLapping

boolean isRobotOverLapping(java.util.List<Robot> robots,
                           Robot robot)
Must be implemented by other classes. This method checks whether robot is overlapping with other Robot(s) on same Plateau. This validation will only be performed when allowRobotOverlap = false.

Parameters:
robots - List of all Robot(s)
robot - Robot for which overlap validation needs to be performed
